# Mental-Health Classifier (Reddit, UK University Context)

A Streamlit web app and research codebase to **detect distress** in Reddit-style posts across five categories:
`neutral`, `academic_stress`, `relationship_issues`, `existential_crisis`, `social_isolation`.

> **Highlights**
> - Models: **TF-IDF + Logistic Regression**, **SVM**, **XGBoost**, **RoBERTa**, and a **Stacked Ensemble**
> - Best performance (hold-out): **Acc 90.16%**, **Macro-F1 0.9064**
> - **Interpretability**: per-class probabilities, severity gauge, word clouds
> - **Actionable support**: optional Cohere suggestions (if API key provided)

